101     | Electronics | 6         | 6/10 = 0.6000
101     | Books       | 2         | 2/10 = 0.2000
101     | Clothing    | 2         | 2/10 = 0.2000
```

All three pass the `>= 0.20` filter.

**`top_products_per_category`** (Electronics):
```
product_id | buyers | category_rank
P10        | 500    | 1
P11        | 450    | 2
P12        | 400    | 3
```

After joining and filtering already-bought:
