## 12. Diversity & Re-Ranking

**"Don't show 15 phones in a row — cap recommendations at 3 per category."**

```sql
WITH raw_recommendations AS (
  -- Assume this comes from any upstream rec CTE
  SELECT
    user_id,
    product_id,
    category,
    recommendation_score,
    -- Global rank ignoring category
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY user_id
      ORDER BY recommendation_score DESC
    ) AS global_rank,
    -- Rank WITHIN each category for this user
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY user_id, category
      ORDER BY recommendation_score DESC
    ) AS category_rank
  FROM recommendations_raw
)
SELECT
  user_id,
  product_id,
  category,
  recommendation_score,
  global_rank,
  category_rank
FROM raw_recommendations
WHERE category_rank <= 3       -- max 3 per category
ORDER BY user_id, recommendation_score DESC;
```

