P1         | Electronics | 95    | 1           | 1
P2         | Electronics | 90    | 2           | 2
P3         | Electronics | 85    | 3           | 3
P4         | Electronics | 80    | 4           | 4   ← FILTERED OUT
P5         | Books       | 75    | 5           | 1
P6         | Books       | 70    | 6           | 2
